## Credits

This project was inspired by the original time control idea from Vladimir Agafonkin (@mourner), creator of Leaflet, core contributor to Mapbox GL JS.

## Third-Party Libraries

This software makes use of the following open-source libraries:

- mediabunny by Yahweasel (MPL-2.0 License)
  JavaScript media toolkit for reading, writing, and converting media files
  https://github.com/Yahweasel/mediabunny - https://mediabunny.dev

- wasm-feature-detect by Google Chrome Labs (Apache-2.0 License)
  https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/wasm-feature-detect

- webm-wasm by Google Chrome Labs (Apache-2.0 License)
  https://github.com/GoogleChromeLabs/webm-wasm

- mp4-h264 package (MIT License)
  Note: H.264 codec may be subject to separate patent licensing by MPEG LA

- MapLibre GL JS (BSD-3-Clause License)
  https://github.com/maplibre/maplibre-gl-js
